,"credit_id":"69540d78bbf5e71732e41a85","department":"Crew","job":"Thanks"},{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":5044340,"known_for_department":"Writing","name":"Linda Rosenkrantz","original_name":"Linda Rosenkrantz","popularity":0.1799,"profile_path":null,"credit_id":"69540d8814228f6d0688e8e1","department":"Crew","job":"Thanks"}]}},"person_59389_translations":{"at":1772689466686,"data":{"id":59389,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Kennedy Rolle","primary":true}}]}},"person_2287564_translations":{"at":1772689475800,"data":{"id":2287564,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"牛莉，中国空军电视艺术中心演员，毕业于解放军艺术学院。\n\n牛莉从影前是名运动员，1986年获得全国第一届女子花样游泳团体冠军。1990年获得全军射击冠军。1991年9月，牛莉首次出演电影《大决战》。2000年6月，主演古装轻喜剧《绝色双娇》。2001年，凭借主演的家庭情感剧《空镜子》提名第22届中国电视剧飞天奖优秀女演员奖。2006年，参演创业励志剧《闯关东》。2011年，主演的相声剧《还钱》获得兔年春晚观众最喜爱的春晚节目小品类一等奖。2013年，凭借主演的家庭伦理剧《新女婿时代》获得首届“央视中国电视剧年度明星盛典”十佳演员称号。2015年，凭借主演的农民史诗剧《老农民》获得第11届中美电影节最佳女主角奖。2017年，主演都市情感电视剧《美好生活》。","name":"牛莉","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Niu Li","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"牛莉，中國空軍電視藝術中心演員，畢業於解放軍藝術學院。\n\n牛莉從影前是名運動員，1986 年獲得全國第一屆女子花樣遊泳團體冠軍。1990 年獲得全軍射擊冠軍。1991 年 9 月，牛莉首次出演電影《大決戰》。2000 年 6 月，主演古裝輕喜劇《絕色雙嬌》。2001 年，憑藉主演的家庭情感劇《空鏡子》提名第 22 屆中國電視劇飛天獎優秀女演員獎。2006 年，參演創業勵志劇《闖關東》。2011 年，主演的相聲劇《還錢》獲得兔年春晚觀眾最喜愛的春晚節目小品類一等獎。2013 年，憑藉主演的家庭倫理劇《新女婿時代》獲得首屆“央視中國電視劇年度明星盛典”十佳演員稱號。2015 年，憑藉主演的農民史詩劇《老農民》獲得第 11 屆中美電影節最佳女主角獎。2017 年，主演都市情感電視劇《美好生活》。","name":"牛莉","primary":false}}]}},"person_2388269_translations":{"at":1772689477997,"data":{"id":2388269,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Miharu Hanai (花井 美春, Hanai Miharu, February 8, 1998) is a Japanese voice actress from Chitose, Hokkaido. She is affiliated with DAX Production. She was formerly affiliated with IAM Agency\n\nAt first, she wanted to join the Takarazuka Revue because she liked singing and expressing herself in front of people, but that dream didn't come true. Later, when she was thinking about her future, she got fascinated after watching the TV anime K-ON! and found a new dream. She then decided to become a voice actress and studied acting at the International Media Gakuin (a subsidiary of the IAM Group). After graduating, she joined IAM Agency and made her debut in 2017 as Sassa Kurasaki in the TV anime Armed Girl's Machiavellism.\n\nShe left IAM Agency on January 31, 2025 and joined DAX Production on April 1.","name":"Miharu Hanai","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"花井美春是日本的女性声优。","name":"花井美春","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"Miharu Hanai (花井 美春, Hanai Miharu, 8 de febrero de 1998) es una actriz de voz japonesa de Chitose, Hokkaido. Está afiliada a DAX Production. Anteriormente perteneció a IAM Agency.\n\nAl principio, quería unirse a Takarazuka Revue porque le gustaba cantar y expresarse frente a la gente. Sin embargo, este sueño no se hizo realidad y mientras pensaba sobre su futuro vio el anime TV y quedó fascinada. Entonces decidió convertirse en seiyuu (actriz de voz) y estudió doblaje en la International Media Gakuin (una filial del Grupo IAM). Después de graduarse, se unió a IAM Agency e hizo su debut en 2017 como Sassa Kurasaki en el anime televisivo Busou Shoujo Machiavellianism.\n\nDejó IAM Agency el 31 de enero de 2025 y se incorporó a DAX Production el 1 de abril del mismo año.","name":"Miharu Hanai","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"花井美春是日本的女性聲優。出身於北海道千歲市，所屬公司為 DAX Production。姊姊為聲優鈴木愛奈。","name":"花井美春","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"花井美春","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"하나이 미하루","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"มิฮารุ ฮานาอิ","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"Miharu Hanai","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Miharu Hanai","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"花井美春是日本的女性聲優，北海道出身。IAM Agency 所屬。姊姊是同為聲優的鈴木愛奈。","name":"花井美春","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Міхару Ханаї","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Михару Ханай","primary":false}}]}},"person_3684746_translations":{"at":1772689483469,"data":{"id":3684746,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Asher Wagh","primary":true}}]}}}}